Package: radsafer
Type: Package
Title: Radiation Safety 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Mark Hogue <mark.hogue@srs.gov>
Maintainer: Mark Hogue <mark.hogue@srs.gov>
Description: Functions for health physics and radiological engineering. Functions include source decay (including Cf-252 sources), analog meter simulation, disk to disk solid angle, and utilities to make MCNP model building simpler.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Suggests: testthat, tidyverse
Imports: ggplot2
URL: https://github.com/markhogue/radsafer
